{% extends "_base.html.j2" %}
{% block content %}
<p>Hi {{ pic | default('there') }},</p>

<p>I see {{ company }} has shipped <strong>{{ total_shipment | default('multiple') }} containers</strong> recently on the {{ pol | default('Vietnam') }} → {{ destination | default('US') }} lane. With that volume, you likely qualify for our VIP contract rates.</p>

<p>Our volume-tiered pricing can typically save <strong>$100-300 per container</strong> compared to spot market rates. The more you ship, the better the rate.</p>

{% if rates %}
<p>Current VIP rates on your lane:</p>
<table style="border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;margin:15px 0">
<tr style="background:#e8f5e9"><th style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:left">Route</th><th style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd">40HQ Rate</th><th style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd">Valid Until</th></tr>
{% for rate in rates[:3] %}
<tr><td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd">{{ rate.pol }} → {{ rate.pod }}</td><td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:center;color:#2e7d32"><strong>${{ rate.amount }}</strong></td><td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:center">{{ rate.exp }}</td></tr>
{% endfor %}
</table>
{% endif %}

<p>Interested in a volume quote? Just let me know your monthly TEU and preferred lanes.</p>

<p>Regards,</p>
{% endblock %}
